SECTION 12: ATTRIBUTION MAPPING

Track which positioning idea leads to adoption:

For each user activation, attribute to:
• Which positioning idea they first saw (ad, content, email)
• Which dashboard feature they used first
• Which insight they found most valuable
• Which insights drove hiring decisions

BUILD MATRIX:
Positioning Idea → Content Type → Traffic Source → Feature Trial → Adoption → Retention

Example: "See Talent Before Competitors" → YouTube video → LinkedIn → 
Dashboard trial → Used "Emerging Talent Alerts" → Hired from alerts → Retained

