SECTION 14: QUICK-WIN MESSAGING TEMPLATES

Template 1: COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGE POSITIONING
"[Company] started using dashboard and found top talent 30 days before competitors. 
That's enough time to hire them all. Result: They're now hiring 2x faster than competition."

Template 2: TIME SAVINGS POSITIONING
"Dashboard found [Recruiter]'s ideal candidate in 5 minutes. 
Manually would have taken 2 hours. That's 95% time savings per hire. 
× 50 hires/year = 75 hours saved annually = 2 weeks of recruiter time."

Template 3: QUALITY IMPROVEMENT POSITIONING
"[Company] switched to dashboard recommendations. 
Result: 92% success rate vs 45% manual hiring. 
Better candidates + lower cost = [Amount] annual savings."

Template 4: RISK REDUCTION POSITIONING
"Dashboard predicted this hire would fail with 94% accuracy. 
Company avoided $2,50,000 bad hire cost. 
One bad hire prevented = dashboard pays for itself forever."

Template 5: STRATEGIC ADVANTAGE POSITIONING
"[HR Leader] used dashboard to forecast AI talent shortage 60 days in advance. 
Company started recruiting early. Got 50 engineers before shortage hit. 
Competitors were stuck with overpriced, unavailable talent."

